race.comment: KISSES FOR GRAN (1) was in the placings last time but shapes well for this on her outstanding win the start prior, getting around this track over 457m in 25.28. Can measure up on top win two back. EXTREME TENSION (5) has a strong record this track and trip with four wins and four placings from 12 starts. In the money last time at this track (25.35) in a Grade 3/4, finishing a 4.5 lengths second. Makes strong appeal on best. CHASING SNOW (2) has been mixing form lately, hitting the frame two back before finishing fourth (25.67) at this track in a Grade 3/4. Key player on best and worth another try. GOLDSTAR JASPER (3) can finish much closer after missing a cheque at this track last start.
